\begin{flushleft}
\section*{Summary}
This financial report covers income and expenditure by EACRC during its fourth full year of operation, from the beginning of February 2019 to the end of January 2020. 

As in all previous years, all work done by members to keep the club running has been done voluntarily, with no payment involved. 

Overview of financial landmarks each year so far:
\begin{itemize}
    \item 2015-17
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Stag, SportScotland \& Edinburgh airport funding
        \item Build \& launch Skelf
        \item Peak adult membership: 40
    \end{itemize}
    \item 2017-18
        \begin{itemize}
        \item Sport for All funding
        \item Purchase 2nd boat kit
        \item Peak adult membership: 61
    \end{itemize}
    \item 2018-19
        \begin{itemize}
        \item Edinburgh airport, Edinburgh council (local area partnership) \& trust funding
        \item External 2nd boat build, launch Sprite \& move to Bellfield
        \item Peak adult membership: 55
    \end{itemize}
\end{itemize}

Income (\pounds9,285.05) and expenditure (\pounds7,616.96) during the year to end Jan 2020 is summarised by category in the figures below. 

