\section*{Income}
Membership supplied just over half of the club's 'income' for the year as a whole. Excluding the previous year's carry over and money received in lieu of pre-paid kit purchases, circuits training sessions and social tickets it was 91\% of the club's income for the year. 

The table compares this year's total to the previous year. The most significant difference is accounted for by the funds received for purchase of our second boat (most of the opening bank balance). 
 
